## Set up .env file

Open .env file on your favorite code editor, and copy paste this code below :

```
DB_HOST= YOUR_DB_HOST
DB_USER= YOUR_DB_USER
DB_PASSWORD= YOUR_DB_PASSWORD
DB_DATABASE= YOUR_DATABASE

PORT=YOUR_PORT

JWT_KEY =YOUR_JWT_KEY
```
